{"word":"G5310 - ὕψιστος - hýpsistos - hoop'-sis-tos - Most high","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὕψιστος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hýpsistos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoop'-sis-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Most high</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"உன்னதமாய் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"highest, most high"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Superlative from the base of <a href=\"#/G5311 - ὕψος - hýpsos - hoop'-sos/5311\">G5311</a>; <i>highest</i>, that is, (masculine singular) the <i>Supreme</i> (God), or (neuter plural) the <i>heavens:</i> - most high, highest.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5251/5251\">G5251</a>, <a href=\"#/G5310/5310\">G5310</a>, <a href=\"#/G5311/5311\">G5311</a>, <a href=\"#/G5312/5312\">G5312</a>, <a href=\"#/G5313/5313\">G5313</a>"}]}